      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments by a second analyst not involved in original model construction.",
      "rationale": "Model setup independently reviewed by a second FDA engineer. Boundary conditions, contact definitions, and material assignments verified against the ASTM F1717 test standard. No discrepancies found. Required level met."
