    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted in the regulatory context because ASTM F1717 is the governing standard for this submission and the single-load-case limitation is explicitly acknowledged. Quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, QoI difference <10%) are met for all three quantities of interest across N=11 constructs and two independent laboratories. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the medium-assurance-level decision for this Class II device.",
